  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Task Processing \u2014 Self-Hosted Only",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "\nTemporal's **internal engine** processing background tasks (`TransferActive`, `TimerActive`) that\ngenerate work for polling workers. Watch **TransferActive vs TimerActive independently** \u2014 a\nbacklog in either stalls workflow progress even when the frontend looks healthy.\n\nUses OSS `ShardInfo` lock latency + `HistoryCacheGetOrCreate` cache latency.\n\n> **Self-hosted only \u2014 permanently.** These are internals below the customer-facing API\n> boundary (history engine task processing, shard locks, mutable-state cache). Temporal Cloud\n> is a managed control plane and does not expose them to customers, on any topology \u2014 unlike\n> the worker-side backlog gap (see **Temporal Critical Flows \u2014 Worker Fleet & Scaling**),\n> this one never closes. For the metrics that DO work on both Cloud and self-hosted, see the\n> **Temporal Critical Flows** folder instead.\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "History Task Processing",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 6
      },
      "id": 2,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Tasks Processed / sec by Task Type",
      "description": "metric: task_requests. Verify name on your build.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus-kind"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "id": 3,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus-kind"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (operation) (rate(task_requests{operation=~\"TransferActive.*|TimerActive.*\"}[$rate]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
